Package: bayesma
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Meta Analyses in R
Description: Provides Bayesian models for meta-analysis, including
    common-effect and random-effects models, one-stage and two-stage
    approaches, and models to adjust for small sample (publication) bias including bias-correction models, selection models, mixture models and PET-PEESE.
